OL,6,FA consultant gynaecologist deemed 'fit
OL,7,Fto practise' by a UK tribunal
OL,8,Ffollowing 24 proven instances of
OL,9,Finappropriate behaviour while working
OL,10,Fin Guernsey would not have been
OL,11,Foffered a job now, given the evidence
OL,12,Fagainst him.
OL,14,FThe Chair of the island's Medical
OL,15,FSpecialist Group, Dr Steve Evans, made
OL,16,Fthe comments after Dr Ali Shokouh-
OL,17,FAmiri was found to have acted
OL,18,Fimproperly, including removing two
OL,19,Fpatients' ovaries without consent and
OL,20,Fkissing another patient.
