OL,6,FDr Shokouh-Amiri was given a warning
OL,7,Ffor his conduct by the Medical
OL,8,FPractitioners Tribunal Service which
OL,9,Fstopped short of banning him from the
OL,10,Fprofession and he currently works at
OL,11,FSouthend Hospital in Essex as a senior
OL,12,Fstaff member.
OL,14,FDr Evans says: "He wouldn't have
OL,15,Fpassed our background checks, given
OL,16,Fthe concerns regarding his practice
OL,17,Fand the fact he's had a warning.
