OL,6,F"Dr Shokouh-Amiri has faced a full
OL,7,Ftribunal hearing by the Medical
OL,8,FPractitioners Tribunal Service
OL,9,Ffollowing allegations while working in
OL,10,Fanother hospital and the decision was
OL,11,Fmade that he is fit to continue
OL,12,Fpractising."
